Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:11:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在一团糟  乔\N{\fs14}{\b0}You're a mess, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别自欺欺人了\N{\fs14}{\b0}You're not fooling anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.69,0:12:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  瑞塔\N{\fs14}{\b0}No, Rita.
