Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,印弟安人吗\N{\fs14}{\b0}Indians, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  正确来说是纳瓦霍人\N{\fs14}{\b0}Navajo, to be exact.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科尔研究了一种新的密码\N{\fs14}{\b0}The Corps has developed a new code...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.71,0:17:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是建立在他们语言的基础上\N{\fs14}{\b0}based on their language.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实有效\N{\fs14}{\b0}It's had quite an impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种东西需要保护\N{\fs14}{\b0}So much so the navy have decided to go to great lengths to protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是你在这里的原因\N{\fs14}{\b0}That's why you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.68,0:17:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要使我们的重要人物安全\N{\fs14}{\b0}You're to pair with one of them, keep his ass safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的工作就是保护他\N{\fs14}{\b0}Your job is to keep him alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以便他能专心工作\N{\fs14}{\b0}so he can do his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请原谅  我觉得我应该做杀鬼子的工作\N{\fs14}{\b0}Begging the major's pardon, but I believe I'd best serve the Corps killing Japs,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是去当谁的保姆\N{\fs14}{\b0}not baby-sitting some Indian.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把你从名单中选出来\N{\fs14}{\b0}Enders, we didn't pick your name out of a hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们需要好的海军陆战队员\N{\fs14}{\b0}We need good marines.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你在这里的原因\N{\fs14}{\b0}That's why you're standing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看一看\N{\fs14}{\b0}Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:17:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一个纳瓦霍人  曾经是\N{\fs14}{\b0}It's a Navajo. Or it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被鬼子抓获拷打致死\N{\fs14}{\b0}Tortured to death by Japanese intelligence trying to bust our code.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸运的是\N{\fs14}{\b0}Fortunately...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他即使想帮也无从帮起\N{\fs14}{\b0}he couldn't help them even if he wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-长官? -他只是一个纳瓦霍人  而不是解译员\N{\fs14}{\b0}-Sir? -Man's a Navajo, not a codetalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密码虽然基于他们的语言 \N{\fs14}{\b0}Code's based on their language...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但仍需要经过培训\N{\fs14}{\b0}but it is still a code.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本人就是想要抓个活的\N{\fs14}{\b0}Tojo would like nothing more than to catch a live one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来告诉你\N{\fs14}{\b0}What I'm about to tell you, Corporal,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管在任何情况下\N{\fs14}{\b0}cannot leave this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解译员不能被敌人活捉\N{\fs14}{\b0}Under no circumstances can you allow your codetalker to fall into enemy hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的任务\N{\fs14}{\b0}Your mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是保护密码\N{\fs14}{\b0}is to protect the code...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜一切代价\N{\fs14}{\b0}at all costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白了吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}You understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我了解\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yes, sir, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs14}{\b0}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你\N{\fs14}{\b0}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚刚升为中士了\N{\fs14}{\b0}You just made sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换你接手\N{\fs14}{\b0}Fortino, take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.12,0:19:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是那个在少校办公室的人吧?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Hey...That was you, right, sitting in front of the major's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是彼得·亨得森\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yeah. Listen, I'm Pete Henderson.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.42,0:20:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们叫我"公牛"  不是因为我四肢发达或什么的\N{\fs14}{\b0}They call me Ox. Not cos of my big muscles or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我来自加州的公牛镇  就在好莱坞北面\N{\fs14}{\b0}I'm from Oxnard, California. Just north of Hollywood a ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也参加贾斯科行动是吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}So you're with JASCO too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.52,0:20:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问第二侦察连在哪里?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Hey, know where we might find 2nd Joint Assault Signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不他妈知道  伙计\N{\fs14}{\b0}No fuckin' idea, mac.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 谢谢你的"美言"\N{\fs14}{\b0}Thanks. Thanks a bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.38,0:20:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从未见过这么多白种人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想他们也从未见过 这么多纳瓦霍人\N{\fs14}{\b0}They've never seen so many Navajo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.29,0:20:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你好象在战场上伤的不轻\N{\fs14}{\b0}Looks to me like you got to see a little action there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.38,0:20:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fs14}{\b0}Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗日的小日本正好打中我的屁股\N{\fs14}{\b0}Jap sons of bitches shot me right in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直不可思议  我当时又没有向后逃跑\N{\fs14}{\b0}You believe that shit? I wasn't running or nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.52,0:21:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在贾斯科行动中的任务 \N{\fs14}{\b0}So, your duty with JASCO
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那些纳瓦霍通讯员有关吗\N{\fs14}{\b0}have anything to do with these Navajo radiomen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.93,0:21:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无可奉告\N{\fs14}{\b0}I'm not at liberty to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你那新的臂章  和我的一样\N{\fs14}{\b0}I see you got a new stripe there. Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你要保守的秘密\N{\fs14}{\b0}So I'm guessing the orders
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我要保守的秘密是一样的\N{\fs14}{\b0}you can't tell me are the same orders I can't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.37,0:21:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都什么玩意儿啊?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Hell of a thing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.18,0:21:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要随便乱说  中士  这是军队\N{\fs14}{\b0}Ain't a democracy, Sergeant. It's the marines.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.06,0:21:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.25,0:21:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们看起来也没什么特别的\N{\fs14}{\b0}They look pretty normal, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.87,0:21:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以为他们会涂上迷彩吗\N{\fs14}{\b0}Expecting them to wear war paint?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我们要介绍一下自己\N{\fs14}{\b0}Maybe we ought to go introduce ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们看来好象迷路了\N{\fs14}{\b0}They look a little lost to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨得森\N{\fs14}{\b0}Henderson.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.46,0:21:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不会跟他们太亲近的\N{\fs14}{\b0}I wouldn't get too friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs14}{\b0}How!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:21:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开个玩笑  我是公牛\N{\fs14}{\b0}Just kiddin'. I'm Ox.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:22:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白马\N{\fs14}{\b0}Whitehorse.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.75,0:22:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫亚奇  本\N{\fs14}{\b0}This is Yahzee. Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.15,0:22:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-下一个  -太棒了 太棒了\N{\fs14}{\b0}-Next. -Beautiful. Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.38,0:22:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭上眼睛吃就会觉得美味了\N{\fs14}{\b0}Close your eyes. It'll taste better.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.24,0:22:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个\N{\fs14}{\b0}Who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.70,0:22:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,介意我和你一起吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Mind if I join you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.39,0:22:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫本 亚奇\N{\fs14}{\b0}I'm Ben Yahzee.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.68,0:22:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像上级让我们俩搭档\N{\fs14}{\b0}Guess the Corps paired us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.78,0:22:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}How you doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.75,0:23:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你挡住我视线了\N{\fs14}{\b0}You're blocking my view.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.81,0:23:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fs14}{\b0}Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.47,0:23:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们把这玩意儿叫什么\N{\fs14}{\b0}What do they call this crap anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.94,0:23:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士兵们叫它狗屎\N{\fs14}{\b0}Marines call it chow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.01,0:23:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来真难吃\N{\fs14}{\b0}Well, there's a propaganda effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.11,0:23:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fs14}{\b0}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.75,0:23:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喝我的吧\N{\fs14}{\b0}You can have mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.44,0:23:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惨了\N{\fs14}{\b0}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.54,0:23:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你叫什么名字\N{\fs14}{\b0}What'd you say your name was again, Private?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.85,0:23:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚奇  本·亚奇\N{\fs14}{\b0}It's Yahzee. Ben Yahzee.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.57,0:23:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿住这个\N{\fs14}{\b0}Hold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.07,0:24:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶\N{\fs14}{\b0}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.52,0:24:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的白人兄弟怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.98,0:24:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很饿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.62,0:24:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一对\N{\fs14}{\b0}I'm in for a couple more.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.27,0:24:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写给你儿子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.06,0:24:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代我向他问候\N{\fs14}{\b0}Tell him I say hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.80,0:24:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小牌  看我怎么吃掉\N{\fs14}{\b0}Pair of cowboys for Big E.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.87,0:24:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该轮到格里克了\N{\fs14}{\b0}Possible straight for the Greek.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.48,0:24:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该翻格里克的底牌了\N{\fs14}{\b0}Possible thumb up the Greek's ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.92,0:24:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙有一对二耶  看来不错\N{\fs14}{\b0}Oh, a pair of twos for the kid. Lookin' good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.56,0:24:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧\N{\fs14}{\b0}Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.06,0:24:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在大举进攻\N{\fs14}{\b0}Now there's a bold move.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.63,0:24:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs14}{\b0}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.33,0:25:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  现在什么情况\N{\fs14}{\b0}OK...Oh, another mess for the Sunshine State.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.37,0:25:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?  你对我不满?\N{\fs14}{\b0}What, are you mad at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.61,0:25:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想赢你的钱\N{\fs14}{\b0}Just want your money.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.06,0:25:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看\N{\fs14}{\b0}Hey! Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.12,0:25:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三条九  漂亮\N{\fs14}{\b0}A trio of nines. Pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.75,0:25:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要下注吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}You shuffle that deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.02,0:25:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs14}{\b0}I certainly did.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.97,0:25:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我加两个筹码压九\N{\fs14}{\b0}Nines bets. I'll raise it two bits.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.30,0:25:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟\N{\fs14}{\b0}Call.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.66,0:25:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翻开底牌\N{\fs14}{\b0}We all got thumbs up our asses.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.90,0:25:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道吗\N{\fs14}{\b0}You won't for much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.14,0:25:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人告诉我下星期我们要动身了\N{\fs14}{\b0}I got a buddy in Intel that says we ship out in a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.48,0:25:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说下个星期说了一个月了\N{\fs14}{\b0}I been hearing "next week" for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.92,0:25:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈利  我不知道你认识什么消息灵通的人\N{\fs14}{\b0}I didn't know you knew anybody in Intelligence, Harri.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.36,0:25:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明年我就退伍了\N{\fs14}{\b0}Next year'd be all right with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.50,0:25:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生们注意了\N{\fs14}{\b0}Gentlemen, read 'em and weep. Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.95,0:25:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三条九带双四\N{\fs14}{\b0}Nines and fours.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.04,0:25:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝贝  全吃了\N{\fs14}{\b0}Full boat, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.70,0:25:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三条K带皇后  你们全挂了\N{\fs14}{\b0}Cowboys over queens. Read 'em and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.46,0:25:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呀\N{\fs14}{\b0}Oh, Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.36,0:25:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈的  我不玩了\N{\fs14}{\b0}Fuck it. I'm out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.69,0:25:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要去给老婆写信了\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yeah. I'm gonna go write the missus.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.03,0:25:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天才知道会发生什么事\N{\fs14}{\b0}God knows what a girl will do without reassurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.28,0:25:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兔崽子\N{\fs14}{\b0}Son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.71,0:26:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还有两个位子  你们来一起玩吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Hey, looks like we got a coupla seats opening up. You wanna come join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.08,0:26:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说真的吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.13,0:26:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,印第安牌手吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}What, Injun poker?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.66,0:26:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们真的会玩吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Hey, how do you boys do that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.60,0:26:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打牌没这么容易\N{\fs14}{\b0}Card on the head,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.47,0:26:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们玩不了\N{\fs14}{\b0}only fool can't see it is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.31,0:26:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想过来玩吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}You want to come on over, or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.49,0:26:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来玩\N{\fs14}{\b0}Cut me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.87,0:26:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs14}{\b0}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.84,0:26:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带两可以\N{\fs14}{\b0}I'm thinkin' Fiery Cross, high-low, hoggers OK,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.27,0:26:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四带一也行\N{\fs14}{\b0}ace plays both ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.31,0:26:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让他没吓着你\N{\fs14}{\b0}Hey, don't let him scare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.32,0:26:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩牌的要诀是\N{\fs14}{\b0}If you've ever played a high-low game,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.29,0:26:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍得花时间和金钱\N{\fs14}{\b0}it's like any other. Waste of time and money.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.23,0:26:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你下什么注?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Well, ante up...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.14,0:26:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酋长?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.84,0:26:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道我是酋长?\N{\fs14}{\b0}How'd you know I was a chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.91,0:26:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又没看过我戴着帽子洗澡\N{\fs14}{\b0}You must've seen me showering with my war bonnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.64,0:27:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快下注  快下注 Deal 'em up   deal 'em up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.82,0:27:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要知道  我们不收贝壳哦\N{\fs14}{\b0} -You know, we don't take wampum here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.49,0:27:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好听\N{\fs14}{\b0}Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.79,0:27:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs14}{\b0}All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.18,0:27:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于下达命令了\N{\fs14}{\b0}Orders finally came through.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.68,0:27:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们明天早上坐船出发\N{\fs14}{\b0}We ship out tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.40,0:27:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的地 塞班岛\N{\fs14}{\b0}Destination: the island of Saipan,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.45,0:27:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们远航到东京的第一站\N{\fs14}{\b0}which is one of the stepping stones we gotta take on our road show to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.82,0:28:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,占领这个岛是很重要的\N{\fs14}{\b0}It's of strategic importance that we capture this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.03,0:28:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将它作为前沿海军基地\N{\fs14}{\b0}We can get ourselves an advanced naval base
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.55,0:28:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以供B-29轰炸机停靠补给\N{\fs14}{\b0}and an airstrip to land and refuel B-29's
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.19,0:28:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后轰炸范围可达东京\N{\fs14}{\b0}and get our bombers within range of Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.89,0:28:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前塞班岛是日本领土\N{\fs14}{\b0}Now, Saipan is Japanese soil,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.76,0:28:18.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有三万人居住\N{\fs14}{\b0}and there's 30,000 of 'em dug in.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.62,0:28:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们定会和我们争夺寸土寸金\N{\fs14}{\b0}They're gonna fight for every square inch,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.08,0:28:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那是他们的家\N{\fs14}{\b0}because it's their home,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.34,0:28:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我们要将他们赶走\N{\fs14}{\b0}but we're gonna take it away from 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.22,0:28:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀掉日本鬼子\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yeah! Kill me some Japs!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.43,0:28:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是这个师的先遣队\N{\fs14}{\b0}We're gonna be in front of the whole damn division.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.17,0:28:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将成为他们眼睛和耳朵\N{\fs14}{\b0}We're gonna be the eyes and the ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.56,0:28:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找出敌军位置\N{\fs14}{\b0}We're gonna be sniffin' out enemy positions,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.35,0:28:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给舰艇火炮提供精确坐标\N{\fs14}{\b0}coordinating the naval gunfire
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.12,0:28:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四个月来  我们正是为此接受训练\N{\fs14}{\b0}exactly what we've been training to do for the last four months.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.99,0:28:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.38,0:28:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是!\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.97,0:29:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指挥部派来几个通讯兵\N{\fs14}{\b0}Now, we got some new radiomen from headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.37,0:29:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白马 \N{\fs14}{\b0}There's a Private Whitehorse...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.90,0:29:11.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和亚奇士官 \N{\fs14}{\b0}and Yahzee...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.22,0:29:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有两位中士\N{\fs14}{\b0}and a couple of sergeants,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.98,0:29:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩德斯\N{\fs14}{\b0}Enders.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.50,0:29:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和亨德森\N{\fs14}{\b0}and Henderson,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.12,0:29:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我正确理解命令的话\N{\fs14}{\b0}who, if I'm understanding these orders correctly,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.64,0:29:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们将保护好我们纳瓦霍伙伴的屁股\N{\fs14}{\b0}will be covering our Navajos' asses.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.00,0:29:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去你的  乔 恩德斯\N{\fs14}{\b0}Goddamn you, Joe Enders!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.21,0:29:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要告诉你们\N{\fs14}{\b0}..but I'm tellin' you,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.59,0:30:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将要踏上敌人的土地\N{\fs14}{\b0}we'll be steppin' into our share of the shit nonetheless.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.82,0:30:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有问题吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.41,0:30:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩德斯\N{\fs14}{\b0}Enders.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.15,0:30:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听上去好像奄奄一息了\N{\fs14}{\b0}Sounds like you're dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.74,0:30:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这能帮助你止吐\N{\fs14}{\b0}These might help get rid of the taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.48,0:30:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查理和我在圣地牙哥搭船时晕船\N{\fs14}{\b0}Charlie and I, we both lost it on the boat ride from San Diego.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.89,0:30:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在亚利桑那遗失了过多水分\N{\fs14}{\b0}Not many bodies of water in Arizona.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.90,0:30:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这玩意儿真有效\N{\fs14}{\b0}Life Savers really helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.27,0:30:42.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想试一颗吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}You want a Life Saver?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.02,0:30:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛来这里?\N{\fs14}{\b0}What are you doin' here?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.20,0:30:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想帮你\N{\fs14}{\b0}Just trying to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.72,0:30:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是问你这个\N{\fs14}{\b0}Not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.78,0:31:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是问我来这参军为了什么?\N{\fs14}{\b0}You mean what am I doing in this uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.57,0:31:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是我的战争\N{\fs14}{\b0}It's my war too, Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.54,0:31:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为我的国家\N{\fs14}{\b0}I'm fighting for my country...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.28,0:31:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为我的土地和同胞而战\N{\fs14}{\b0}for my land, for my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.30,0:31:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不在乎你的同胞\N{\fs14}{\b0}Not your people I'm worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.96,0:31:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着恩德斯\N{\fs14}{\b0}Listen, Enders,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.07,0:31:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是解译员\N{\fs14}{\b0}I'm a codetalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.39,0:31:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要在2分半钟内做完以前要一个小时才能做完的\N{\fs14}{\b0}It takes me two-and-a-half minutes to do what used to take an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.05,0:31:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人说的比你现在说的还要过分\N{\fs14}{\b0}Now, somebody wearing a lot more stripes than you
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.96,0:31:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认为我是为了得到些什么\N{\fs14}{\b0}thinks that's worth something.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.98,0:31:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当子弹从你头顶飞过时  提醒我记一下\N{\fs14}{\b0}Remind me to time you when you got bullets flying over your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.09,0:31:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你究竟是怎么了?\N{\fs14}{\b0}What the hell's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.67,0:31:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs14}{\b0}Shave his belly with a rusty razor
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.59,0:31:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs14}{\b0}Shave his belly with a rusty razor Early in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.35,0:32:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs14}{\b0}From the halls of Montezuma
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.64,0:32:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs14}{\b0}To the shores of Tripoli
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.02,0:32:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs14}{\b0}We will fight our country's battles
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.36,0:32:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs14}{\b0}On the land and on the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.36,0:32:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs14}{\b0}First to fight for right and freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.74,0:32:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs14}{\b0}And to keep our honor clean
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.71,0:32:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs14}{\b0}We are proud to claim the title
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.83,0:32:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs14}{\b0}Of United States Marines
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.70,0:32:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你耳朵好点了吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}How's that ear?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.16,0:32:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你不承认耳朵有问题\N{\fs14}{\b0}Not that you'd ever admit it,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.46,0:32:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但吃几颗药会好过点\N{\fs14}{\b0}but if it starts aching, take a couple of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.58,0:33:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明早给我打个电话\N{\fs14}{\b0}And call me in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.16,0:33:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是明早就要启程了?\N{\fs14}{\b0}You're not gonna be here in the morning, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.28,0:33:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启程前 \N{\fs14}{\b0}Shipping out...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.58,0:33:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不请我喝一杯吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}without even buying me a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.89,0:33:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样强迫 强迫一个当兵的\N{\fs14}{\b0}Ought to be ashamed of yourself, hustling a...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.12,0:33:18.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不羞愧吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}hustling marines.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.10,0:33:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爱喝什么\N{\fs14}{\b0}What's your poison?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.11,0:33:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是来点比较烈的好了\N{\fs14}{\b0}Jeez, might as well go all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.21,0:33:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来一杯吧\N{\fs14}{\b0}I'll get a shot of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.08,0:33:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰姆酒\N{\fs14}{\b0}Rum.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.89,0:33:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃迪  给我来一杯巴卡第(古巴的一种兰姆酒)\N{\fs14}{\b0}Eddie, give me a shot of Bacardi.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.91,0:33:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两杯吧\N{\fs14}{\b0}Make that two.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.56,0:33:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要和我喝吗\N{\fs14}{\b0}May as well join me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.27,0:33:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-当然不是  -好\N{\fs14}{\b0}-Why not? -OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.66,0:33:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs14}{\b0}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.91,0:33:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为战争干杯\N{\fs14}{\b0}Well...to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.63,0:34:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1944年6月16日 日本塞班岛
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.36,0:34:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲啊!冲啊!\N{\fs14}{\b0}Let's go, let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.69,0:34:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让那些家伙分散开\N{\fs14}{\b0}Get those men spread out!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.93,0:34:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查理  跟上跟上\N{\fs14}{\b0}Charlie, come on, come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.24,0:36:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跟上\N{\fs14}{\b0}Come on, keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.81,0:36:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向前冲  向前冲  跟上\N{\fs14}{\b0}Let's go, let's go, let's go! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.71,0:36:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还可以吧!\N{\fs14}{\b0}How am I doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.45,0:36:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得不错\N{\fs14}{\b0}You're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.72,0:36:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家冲啊\N{\fs14}{\b0}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.96,0:36:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟在我后面\N{\fs14}{\b0}Stay on my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.73,0:37:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫你跟在我后面\N{\fs14}{\b0}I told you to stay on my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.14,0:37:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-蹲下  -快走\N{\fs14}{\b0}-Stay low! -Get out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.69,0:37:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧\N{\fs14}{\b0}Go to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.34,0:38:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲\N{\fs14}{\b0}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.96,0:39:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉他出来\N{\fs14}{\b0}Get him outta there!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.63,0:39:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉他出来\N{\fs14}{\b0}Get me outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.81,0:39:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-别动   -快拉他出来\N{\fs14}{\b0}-Hold still, damn it! -Get him outta there!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.95,0:39:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你他妈狗娘养的\N{\fs14}{\b0}You sons of bitches!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.11,0:40:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗堤诺  掩护我\N{\fs14}{\b0}Fortino! Cover me!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.25,0:40:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白马  趴下\N{\fs14}{\b0}Whitehorse, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.77,0:40:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趴下\N{\fs14}{\b0}Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.67,0:40:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕帕斯\N{\fs14}{\b0}Pappas!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.14,0:40:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医护兵\N{\fs14}{\b0}Corpsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.97,0:40:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带上你的钢盔\N{\fs14}{\b0}Helmet goes on your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.38,0:41:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医护兵\N{\fs14}{\b0}Corpsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.72,0:41:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看好他\N{\fs14}{\b0}Take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.09,0:41:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手放这里\N{\fs14}{\b0}Put a hand on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.57,0:41:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坦克  坦克来了\N{\fs14}{\b0}Tank! Tank! Tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.05,0:41:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}You ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.55,0:41:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.28,0:41:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-扔  -扔\N{\fs14}{\b0}-Go! -Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.52,0:41:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喷火枪烧它\N{\fs14}{\b0}Harrigan, light it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.56,0:41:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上  伙计  继续战斗\N{\fs14}{\b0}Let's go, boys! Keep up the fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.46,0:42:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你中弹了吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Are you hit? Are you hit?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.20,0:42:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事  没事没事\N{\fs14}{\b0}You're OK. You're good, you're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.33,0:42:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fs14}{\b0}Are you OK, Chick?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.25,0:42:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如火如茶啊  冈尼\N{\fs14}{\b0}Still in the hunt, Gunny.
