Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.51,0:42:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在  我们没事\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yeah, we're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.79,0:42:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格里克呼吸困难\N{\fs14}{\b0}Greek's predisposed to hyperventilate.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.04,0:42:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs14}{\b0}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.78,0:42:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一兴奋就呼吸困难\N{\fs14}{\b0}I can't breathe when I get excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.72,0:42:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈的  像个娘们\N{\fs14}{\b0}Goddamn! Must be hell on your gal!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.14,0:42:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩德斯  告诉海军方位  轰掉那些碉堡\N{\fs14}{\b0}Enders, get the navy on the horn and tell 'em to dig out those guns.
