Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.86,0:43:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右170  海拔050\N{\fs14}{\b0}right 700. Elevation zero-five-zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.14,0:43:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点转译这该死的坐标\N{\fs14}{\b0}Relay the damn coordinates!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.36,0:43:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利桑那  亚利桑那\N{\fs14}{\b0}Arizona! Arizona!
