Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.92,0:44:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右200 　往上50\N{\fs14}{\b0}Right 200! Up 50.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.36,0:44:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即开火\N{\fs14}{\b0}Fire for effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.04,0:44:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.05,0:45:18.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲啊  冲啊\N{\fs14}{\b0}Let's go! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.30,0:46:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈瑞肯\N{\fs14}{\b0}Harrigan!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.94,0:46:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烧掉那掩体\N{\fs14}{\b0}Torch the box!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.30,0:46:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉他\N{\fs14}{\b0}Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.10,0:47:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的\N{\fs14}{\b0}Goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.61,0:47:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶\N{\fs14}{\b0}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.58,0:47:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内里  带上炸药包\N{\fs14}{\b0}Nellie. Take the satchel charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.37,0:47:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到没\N{\fs14}{\b0}You hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.52,0:47:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去\N{\fs14}{\b0}Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.21,0:47:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们会掩护我  是吧?\N{\fs14}{\b0}You're gonna cover me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.90,0:47:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你去那边  左翼包抄\N{\fs14}{\b0}I'll go with you. We flank left.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.66,0:47:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会用烟雾弹掩护你的\N{\fs14}{\b0}I'll cover you. Smoke and cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.90,0:47:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以做到的\N{\fs14}{\b0}I can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.57,0:47:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以做到的\N{\fs14}{\b0}I can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.61,0:48:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烟雾弹\N{\fs14}{\b0}Smoke 'em up!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.77,0:48:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里\N{\fs14}{\b0}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.81,0:48:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掩护他\N{\fs14}{\b0}Cover up.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.87,0:49:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽\N{\fs14}{\b0}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.17,0:49:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽  他妈的日本队达阵\N{\fs14}{\b0}Shit. Goddamn Nipponese touchdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.01,0:49:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前进大约0500
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.65,0:49:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时会有替换人员及弹药补给  完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.56,0:49:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到  确保他们有新的密码
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.19,0:49:37.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[风」回答 [语者」
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.32,0:49:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们兄弟称呼我们的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.64,0:49:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说怎么样  完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.64,0:49:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[风语者」  我挺喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.21,0:49:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  凯莫 赛比今晚小心行事  完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.44,0:49:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么可以把干粮吃完\N{\fs14}{\b0}Biscuits? How can you ruin biscuits?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.54,0:49:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王八蛋  你在发什么牢骚呀\N{\fs14}{\b0}You are a whiny son of a bitch right now, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.13,0:50:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在丛林里呆上2200小时  这在东海岸怎么可能做到?\N{\fs14}{\b0}2200 hours in jungle hell -what does that make it on the East Coast?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.85,0:50:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么他妈知道?\N{\fs14}{\b0}How the fucking hell should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.35,0:50:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在才七点\N{\fs14}{\b0}Just seven...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.96,0:50:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期天早上八点了\N{\fs14}{\b0}It's 8am, Sunday morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.54,0:50:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望我的床在礼拜六晚上不会被其他男人占据\N{\fs14}{\b0}I hope my side of the bed didn't get taken up Saturday night.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.66,0:50:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内尔  你怕自己戴了绿帽  你在担心她吧\N{\fs14}{\b0}Nell, you'll give yourself an ulcer, you keep worrying about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.41,0:50:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我回到罗得岛就被戴了绿帽\N{\fs14}{\b0}Might get my ass sent back to Rhody, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.74,0:50:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内尔  罗得岛上还有很多女人呀\N{\fs14}{\b0}There's plenty of dollies outside of Rhode Island, Nell.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.10,0:50:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多喔\N{\fs14}{\b0}Many plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.17,0:50:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不像这个鸟地方\N{\fs14}{\b0}Well, there sure as shit ain't any here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.34,0:50:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿不是真的\N{\fs14}{\b0}Ain't that the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.69,0:50:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗得岛上的女孩\N{\fs14}{\b0}That's cos they're all in Daytona Beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.85,0:50:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,常去戴脱那海滩\N{\fs14}{\b0}The most beautiful women...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.99,0:50:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮马子多\N{\fs14}{\b0}in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.99,0:50:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在战争之前\N{\fs14}{\b0}This one time,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.18,0:50:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一次\N{\fs14}{\b0}before the war,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.81,0:50:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我躺在沙滩上\N{\fs14}{\b0}I'm lyin' on the beach...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.67,0:50:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个可爱的家伙  叫莫莉\N{\fs14}{\b0}and this sweet little thing named Molly...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.86,0:50:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从水边一直向我走来\N{\fs14}{\b0}comes out the water.She walks straight up to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.45,0:50:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问我是不是饿了\N{\fs14}{\b0}and asks me if I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.01,0:50:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她有根小香肠\N{\fs14}{\b0}cos she's havin' a weenie roast.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.53,0:50:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放屁\N{\fs14}{\b0}Shit! Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.97,0:50:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  她是男的\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yeah, me and Molly, oh boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.48,0:51:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在全身上下只剩下Zippo打火机\N{\fs14}{\b0}Now I'm on Saipan with this giant Zippo strapped to my back
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.48,0:51:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我常这么嘲笑自己\N{\fs14}{\b0}and I'm roastin' human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.95,0:51:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么自愿从军\N{\fs14}{\b0}Why I volunteered...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.07,0:51:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我孑然一生\N{\fs14}{\b0}beyond me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.14,0:51:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为自己在这里而自豪\N{\fs14}{\b0}Damn, I'm proud to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.63,0:51:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我全家都参军了\N{\fs14}{\b0}My whole family's been in the Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.01,0:51:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家老头子被判无期徒刑\N{\fs14}{\b0}My old man, he's a lifer.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.27,0:51:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论在哪里\N{\fs14}{\b0}An ass-kicker on the land and on the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.48,0:51:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至在家乡都让人看不起\N{\fs14}{\b0}Around the house too.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.14,0:51:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许现在他被释放了\N{\fs14}{\b0}Maybe now he'll back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.63,0:51:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕帕斯  我 \N{\fs14}{\b0}Pappas, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.29,0:51:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想请你帮我个忙\N{\fs14}{\b0}I want you to do me a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.65,0:51:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一我有个三长两短\N{\fs14}{\b0}If anything should happen to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.01,0:51:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个给我妻子\N{\fs14}{\b0}you make sure that my wife gets this.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.39,0:52:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确保她拿到手\N{\fs14}{\b0}I mean, she picked them out and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.10,0:52:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说这些  内尔\N{\fs14}{\b0}Don't talk like that, Nell.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.53,0:52:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要开这种玩笑\N{\fs14}{\b0}You don't even joke about shit like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.82,0:52:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把戒指戴上  你能回家的\N{\fs14}{\b0}Now you put that ring back on. You're goin' home.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.75,0:52:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(印地安语)
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.29,0:53:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尝尝这个\N{\fs14}{\b0}Don't thank me till you've tried it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.73,0:53:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你掉的信\N{\fs14}{\b0}You missed mail call.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.72,0:53:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在干什么?\N{\fs14}{\b0}What the hell are they doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.48,0:53:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道\N{\fs14}{\b0}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.59,0:53:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从太阳下山就开始了\N{\fs14}{\b0}They've been doin' it since sundown.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.13,0:53:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是祈福的一种吧\N{\fs14}{\b0}Sounds like some kind of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.68,0:53:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许他们知道我们的任务\N{\fs14}{\b0}Maybe they know our orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.69,0:54:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你下得了手吗  乔?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Think you could do it, Joe?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.52,0:54:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束这个话题  亨德森\N{\fs14}{\b0}Give it a rest, Henderson.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.10,0:54:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束话题?  我试着不去谈  可是 \N{\fs14}{\b0}Give it a rest? I keep tryin', but...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.76,0:54:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来杀鬼子的  不是自己人\N{\fs14}{\b0}I'm here to kill Japs, not marines.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.80,0:54:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚奇  你是个勇士
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.03,0:54:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的家人将以你为荣
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.23,0:55:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小子  你在这儿干什么?\N{\fs14}{\b0}What the hell you think you're doin', boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.91,0:55:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿我的军服\N{\fs14}{\b0}Getting on my uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.13,0:55:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚奇  你知道你和日本人有什么区别吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}You know the difference between you and a Jap, Yahzee?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.66,0:55:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制服上的区别\N{\fs14}{\b0}It's that uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.26,0:55:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样\N{\fs14}{\b0}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.85,0:55:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我了解你们\N{\fs14}{\b0}See, I know you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.05,0:55:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你们这种人有多野蛮  小子\N{\fs14}{\b0}I know what kind of slanty-eyed savage you are, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.00,0:55:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单独一个在这儿可得小心\N{\fs14}{\b0}You ought to be careful out here all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.48,0:55:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人会保护你\N{\fs14}{\b0}No baby-sitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.99,0:55:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也许会把你当作日本人\N{\fs14}{\b0}I might just take you for a Jap.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.66,0:55:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇克  总得让我穿上衣服吧\N{\fs14}{\b0}You gonna let me get dressed, Chick?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.42,0:55:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是你还要继续你这个无聊的举动\N{\fs14}{\b0}Or keep demonstrating what an ignorant fool you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.64,0:56:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无聊的举动那又怎么样\N{\fs14}{\b0}How's that for an ignorant fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.91,0:56:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来啊\N{\fs14}{\b0}Go ahead, try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.46,0:56:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想干嘛?\N{\fs14}{\b0}You gonna do somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.29,0:57:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇克  住手\N{\fs14}{\b0}Chick! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.38,0:57:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪开\N{\fs14}{\b0}Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.45,0:57:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧  本?\N{\fs14}{\b0}You OK, Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.03,0:57:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯!\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.10,0:57:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本?  妈的\N{\fs14}{\b0}Ben? Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.92,0:57:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为他是日本人  陆战队员都会穿制服\N{\fs14}{\b0}I thought he was a Jap. You know, killed some marine for that uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.31,0:57:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了  奇克\N{\fs14}{\b0}Sure you did, Chick.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.62,0:57:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个他妈的印地安人  看起来像日本人\N{\fs14}{\b0}Damn Injun looks just like a Jap, don't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.72,0:57:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是他妈的印地安人\N{\fs14}{\b0}Look, I'm no damn Injun.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.18,0:57:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是塔房部落\N{\fs14}{\b0}I'm Navajo...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.83,0:57:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苦水族的纳瓦霍人\N{\fs14}{\b0}of the Bitter Water People, born for the Towering House clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.62,0:57:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你确实长得像小日本\N{\fs14}{\b0}But you do look like a Nip.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.84,0:57:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次你要洗澡事先告知我\N{\fs14}{\b0}Next time you decide to take a bath, Private, let me know,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.30,0:57:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我就踹你屁股\N{\fs14}{\b0}or I'll kick your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.91,0:58:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐东西\N{\fs14}{\b0}Fuckin' shitbird.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.66,0:58:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候了  还像个娘们\N{\fs14}{\b0}Supposed to be with a baby-sitter all the time, I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.41,0:58:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里勾心斗角\N{\fs14}{\b0}Out here huntin' salmon and shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.96,0:58:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚他们那个仪式\N{\fs14}{\b0}That ceremony you saw last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.31,0:58:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做辟邪仪式\N{\fs14}{\b0}It's called a protection ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.42,0:58:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纳瓦霍人相信  在人快死前\N{\fs14}{\b0}Navajo believe, until a body's given a proper burial,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.75,0:58:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶灵也就是我们所称的魔鬼\N{\fs14}{\b0}the spirits stay near it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.36,0:58:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会围绕在身边\N{\fs14}{\b0}Chindis -that's what we call evil spirits. Demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.01,0:58:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从小就不把这当回事\N{\fs14}{\b0}I haven't thought much about it since I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.96,0:58:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到我看到那些尸体\N{\fs14}{\b0}Till I saw those dead bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.65,0:58:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说你看到鬼魂了?\N{\fs14}{\b0}You telling me you saw ghosts, Private?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.34,0:58:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  中士  我是说我不会再发愣了\N{\fs14}{\b0}No, Sergeant. I'm telling you I won't freeze up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.18,0:58:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你的伙伴在你的前额涂上灰烬\N{\fs14}{\b0}Because your buddy smeared ash on your forehead?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.20,0:58:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs14}{\b0}That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.25,0:58:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我的伙伴在我的前额涂上灰烬\N{\fs14}{\b0}Cos my buddy smeared ash on my forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.24,0:59:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你见过鬼魂吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}You ever see ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.22,0:59:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再问这样愚蠢的问题了\N{\fs14}{\b0}No more stupid questions today, Private.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.80,0:59:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是命令\N{\fs14}{\b0}That's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.73,0:59:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很美的音乐\N{\fs14}{\b0}Sounds beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.24,0:59:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是自学的吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}You, uh, you self-taught?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.09,0:59:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父亲教的\N{\fs14}{\b0}My dad was always playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.20,0:59:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道他们说什么吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}You know what they say:
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.43,0:59:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说你吹不赢他们的\N{\fs14}{\b0}if you can't beat 'em...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.50,0:59:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说\N{\fs14}{\b0}No shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.60,0:59:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父亲给了我这个东西\N{\fs14}{\b0}My dad, he...he gave me this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.94,1:00:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是口琴\N{\fs14}{\b0}Used to call me the Pied Piper of the Pigs.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.04,1:00:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我吹奏它的时候我总觉得很单调\N{\fs14}{\b0}Used to bring 'em in for feeding with this little tune I played.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.53,1:00:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我又不能向你借笛子吹  那么 \N{\fs14}{\b0}I know I ain't gonna get you to quit playin' that thing, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.85,1:00:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如我替你伴奏吧\N{\fs14}{\b0}like you just said, if you can't beat 'em...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.53,1:00:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想没什么用吧\N{\fs14}{\b0}I don't think it's gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.28,1:00:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我们也没什么事做  不如就来试看看  怎样?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Well, we ain't got much else to do out here.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.61,1:00:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样?\N{\fs14}{\b0}What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.60,1:00:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs14}{\b0}OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.00,1:00:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你吹旋律\N{\fs14}{\b0}All right, you lead off.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.31,1:00:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟着你\N{\fs14}{\b0}I'll follow you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.54,1:01:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二侦察连在0600位置出发
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.84,1:01:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沿190约克附近04公路进行侦察任务
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.07,1:01:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在树林西北方 可能会遭遇轻微抵抗  完毕
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.94,1:01:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到  轻微是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.37,1:01:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有抵抗是轻微的  完毕
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.22,1:01:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住   我们的任务不是问个不停
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.34,1:01:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是照做或战死  完毕
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.89,1:01:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的乔  你好吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Dear Joe, how the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.96,1:01:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不爱写信  我也不期望你会回\N{\fs14}{\b0}Or, given that you're not much of a writer, should I not expect an answer?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.54,1:01:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报纸说我们的士兵很英勇\N{\fs14}{\b0}The newspapers say our boys are doing great.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.61,1:01:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能记者没有去卡内奥赫湾海军医院看过\N{\fs14}{\b0}But I don't think the reporters have been to Kaneohe Bay Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.16,1:01:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最近在怀基基海滩发现一只流浪狗\N{\fs14}{\b0}I found a stray dog the other day on Waikiki.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.36,1:01:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我收留了它并给它洗澡\N{\fs14}{\b0}I gave him a bath and took him in.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.17,1:01:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它让我想起了你  很可爱\N{\fs14}{\b0}He reminded me of you -but cuter.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.62,1:02:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏有它在寒风中给我温暖\N{\fs14}{\b0}At least he keeps me warm at night.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.30,1:02:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试着不去想你\N{\fs14}{\b0}I try not to think about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.78,1:02:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那里会发生的事\N{\fs14}{\b0}About what might be happening over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.79,1:02:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有时我躺在床上\N{\fs14}{\b0}But sometimes, when I'm lying in bed,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.21,1:02:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不自觉的会想你在哪里\N{\fs14}{\b0}I can't keep myself from wondering where you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.56,1:02:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在做什么\N{\fs14}{\b0}How you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.02,1:02:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么\N{\fs14}{\b0}What the hell you doin'?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.56,1:02:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我儿子写信\N{\fs14}{\b0}Writing a letter to my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.15,1:02:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没听到命令吗\N{\fs14}{\b0}Forget your orders?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.60,1:02:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能送信出去\N{\fs14}{\b0}No letters out.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.38,1:02:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邮递不通\N{\fs14}{\b0}Command don't want postmarks going to the reservation.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.21,1:02:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿!你没听见吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Hey! You hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.74,1:02:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算回家后再给他看\N{\fs14}{\b0}I thought that he might read 'em when I get home.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.81,1:03:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你儿子\N{\fs14}{\b0}What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.99,1:03:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫什么?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Your son.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.27,1:03:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔治  乔治 华盛顿\N{\fs14}{\b0}It's George. George Washington.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.82,1:03:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔治 华盛顿 亚奇\N{\fs14}{\b0}George Washington Yahzee.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.24,1:03:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他长大后应该会很有成就\N{\fs14}{\b0}It's got a bit of a ring to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.90,1:03:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太太可不这么想\N{\fs14}{\b0}My wife wasn't so sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.29,1:03:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她有点传统\N{\fs14}{\b0}She's a little more traditional.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.50,1:03:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-感觉很和睦的家庭　　-亚奇  也让我们看看\N{\fs14}{\b0}-Nice-looking family. -Let's see, Yahz.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.84,1:03:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是乔治  他很有个性\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yeah, that George, he's quite a character.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.68,1:03:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他自己有主见\N{\fs14}{\b0}He's got a mind of his own.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.35,1:03:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以抽一根吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Can I try one of those?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.23,1:03:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你抽烟?\N{\fs14}{\b0}You smoke?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.79,1:03:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不怎么抽\N{\fs14}{\b0}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.70,1:04:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-下车  -快下车\N{\fs14}{\b0}-Dismount! -Get out of the truck!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.42,1:04:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快\N{\fs14}{\b0}Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.34,1:04:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来\N{\fs14}{\b0}Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.29,1:04:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走\N{\fs14}{\b0}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.35,1:04:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我中弹了\N{\fs14}{\b0}I'm hit!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.38,1:04:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚奇\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yahzee!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.54,1:04:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚奇\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yahzee!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.40,1:04:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我中弹了\N{\fs14}{\b0}I'm hit!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.56,1:04:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它烧起来了  脱下它\N{\fs14}{\b0}Take it off! It burns!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.05,1:04:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没受伤  闭嘴  你没事\N{\fs14}{\b0}You're not hit. Just shut up. You're not hit.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.22,1:05:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散开\N{\fs14}{\b0}Spread out!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.43,1:05:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走\N{\fs14}{\b0}Move!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.30,1:05:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趴下\N{\fs14}{\b0}Get down.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.64,1:05:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们从哪里来的?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Where the hell are they comin' from?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.10,1:05:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从我们那里\N{\fs14}{\b0}From us.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.85,1:05:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs14}{\b0}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.14,1:05:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是日本大炮\N{\fs14}{\b0}They're not Jap guns.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.45,1:05:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们被友军误袭?\N{\fs14}{\b0}We're getting shot at by our own guys?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.47,1:05:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们应该在04公路的\N{\fs14}{\b0}We're supposed to be on road 04.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.69,1:05:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-打开无线电  -不行\N{\fs14}{\b0}-Get the regiment on the horn. -I can't!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.29,1:05:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉总部我们被 \N{\fs14}{\b0}Tell 'em they're shelling...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.94,1:05:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  无线电被打坏了\N{\fs14}{\b0}I can't! The radio's out. It's been hit.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.94,1:05:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-火力太密集了  -鬼子们应该就在我们前面\N{\fs14}{\b0}-They're firing too short! -The Japs gotta be way ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.47,1:05:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做点什么吧\N{\fs14}{\b0}Do somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.42,1:05:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  跟我来\N{\fs14}{\b0}Shit...Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.67,1:05:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们走错路了  -他妈的\N{\fs14}{\b0}-We're on the wrong fuckin' road! -Goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.50,1:06:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\fs14}{\b0}God.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.79,1:06:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗娘养的\N{\fs14}{\b0}Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.18,1:07:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来救你  伙计\N{\fs14}{\b0}I got you, mac!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.36,1:07:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医护兵\N{\fs14}{\b0}Corpsman!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.95,1:07:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医护兵\N{\fs14}{\b0}Corpsman!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.03,1:07:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医护兵\N{\fs14}{\b0}Corpsman!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.80,1:07:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内里\N{\fs14}{\b0}Nellie!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.19,1:07:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医护兵\N{\fs14}{\b0}Corpsman!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.60,1:08:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔 你说得对\N{\fs14}{\b0}You were right, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.85,1:08:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的跟他们长得很像\N{\fs14}{\b0}I do look like a Nip.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.49,1:08:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么意思?\N{\fs14}{\b0}What the hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.74,1:08:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿日本军服混进去  \N{\fs14}{\b0}Putting on that Jap uniform
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.62,1:08:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去抢一台无线电来请求火力支援\N{\fs14}{\b0}Trying to get one of their radios, call off our guns.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.39,1:08:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太蠢了\N{\fs14}{\b0}That's stupid.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.04,1:08:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴  让他说\N{\fs14}{\b0}Shut up. Let him talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.89,1:08:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让他去的\N{\fs14}{\b0}He's not goin' out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.94,1:08:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是指挥  恩德斯\N{\fs14}{\b0}You're not in charge here, Enders.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.12,1:08:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接到命令  他归我管\N{\fs14}{\b0}I got orders, Gunny. He's my responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.60,1:08:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只是个孩子\N{\fs14}{\b0}He's just a kid!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.35,1:08:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们杀了自己人!\N{\fs14}{\b0}You killed your own!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.59,1:08:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是怎么回事!\N{\fs14}{\b0}What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.54,1:08:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们杀了自己人!\N{\fs14}{\b0}You killed your own!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.99,1:08:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王八蛋!\N{\fs14}{\b0}Sons of bitches!You killed your own!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.38,1:08:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们杀了自己人!\N{\fs14}{\b0}Sons of bitches!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.31,1:08:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定要做吗\N{\fs14}{\b0}Sure you're up to this?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.65,1:09:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽快完成任务  长官\N{\fs14}{\b0}Find out soon enough, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.83,1:09:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么\N{\fs14}{\b0}What the hell are you doin' there?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.30,1:09:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟他一起去\N{\fs14}{\b0}I'm goin' with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.84,1:09:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没意见吧\N{\fs14}{\b0}If that's OK with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.72,1:09:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枪给我\N{\fs14}{\b0}Give me the rifle.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.68,1:09:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Horyo-da.(日语战俘的叫法)
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.92,1:09:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是日语中战俘的意思\N{\fs14}{\b0}It's Jap for prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.60,1:09:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家准备好\N{\fs14}{\b0}All right, everybody be ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.05,1:10:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲啊!\N{\fs14}{\b0}Now!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.04,1:11:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打我  打我\N{\fs14}{\b0}Hit me. Hit me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.41,1:11:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饶了我吧\N{\fs14}{\b0}Please don't hit me!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.08,1:11:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚奇\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yahzee!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.53,1:12:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他\N{\fs14}{\b0}Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.05,1:12:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他妈的杀了他\N{\fs14}{\b0}Goddamn it, kill him!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.69,1:12:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快用无线电\N{\fs14}{\b0}Get on the radio!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.17,1:12:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白鲍维  白鲍维\N{\fs14}{\b0}Bowie White, Bowie White.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.30,1:12:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是红卡逊\N{\fs14}{\b0}this is Carson Red!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.91,1:12:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停火  停火  打到自己人了\N{\fs14}{\b0}Cease fire! Cease fire! You're shelling marines!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.71,1:12:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中士\N{\fs14}{\b0}Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.06,1:12:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停火  停火\N{\fs14}{\b0}Cease fire! Cease fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.64,1:12:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,325　543  攻击这方位\N{\fs14}{\b0}Add 325, fire for effect!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.59,1:13:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调整方位　325　攻击这方位\N{\fs14}{\b0}Redirect fire. Add 325, fire for effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.03,1:13:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们快离开\N{\fs14}{\b0}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.32,1:13:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,升高  快点  开火\N{\fs14}{\b0}Crank it up! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.61,1:13:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备\N{\fs14}{\b0}Commence fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.40,1:13:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开火\N{\fs14}{\b0}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.92,1:13:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.70,1:13:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不赖\N{\fs14}{\b0}Well, I'll be.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.03,1:13:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上校  有什么能帮你的吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Colonel. Can I help you, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.05,1:13:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在找我们的一个中士  恩德斯  约瑟夫·恩德斯\N{\fs14}{\b0}I'm looking for Sergeant Enders. Joseph F Enders.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.83,1:13:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩德斯\N{\fs14}{\b0}Enders.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.33,1:14:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在  长官\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.19,1:14:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报告说你越权指挥上级\N{\fs14}{\b0}Report I read claims you went above and beyond.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.84,1:14:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.80,1:14:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你的英勇事迹  我们还是认为应该奖励\N{\fs14}{\b0}You've been recommended for commendation.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.21,1:14:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我注意了一下\N{\fs14}{\b0}And I concur.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.08,1:14:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没看到适合授勋的地方\N{\fs14}{\b0}But I don't see any point in you having to wait around
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.75,1:14:26.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就不要拘泥于形式\N{\fs14}{\b0}for all those formalities to work themselves out.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.95,1:14:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我亲自为你戴上吧\N{\fs14}{\b0}Not when I got one of these handy.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.65,1:14:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你\N{\fs14}{\b0}Congratulations, Enders.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.17,1:14:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你救了很多战友\N{\fs14}{\b0}You saved a lot of marines.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.44,1:14:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官  非我一人  \N{\fs14}{\b0}I wasn't alone in that, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.01,1:14:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有本 亚吉  我无法成功\N{\fs14}{\b0}I couldn't have done it without Private Ben Yahzee.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.29,1:14:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fs14}{\b0}Oh...Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.54,1:14:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,印第安人\N{\fs14}{\b0}The, uh, Indian.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.93,1:14:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上校  请原谅  他是塔房部落\N{\fs14}{\b0}Begging the colonel's pardon, he's a Navajo, of the Bitter Water People,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.05,1:15:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苦水族的纳瓦霍人\N{\fs14}{\b0}born for the Towering House clan.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.61,1:15:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  塔房部落\N{\fs14}{\b0}Of course. Navajo.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.47,1:15:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纳瓦霍人\N{\fs14}{\b0}Towering House clan.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.58,1:15:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续努力  恩德斯\N{\fs14}{\b0}You keep up the good work, Enders.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.44,1:15:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它交给内里的太太\N{\fs14}{\b0}Send that to Nellie's wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.00,1:16:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩德斯   这是你的信吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}You ever not miss mail call, Enders?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.98,1:16:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈说如果有人花时间精力写信给你\N{\fs14}{\b0}My mom says somebody takes the time to write a letter,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.66,1:16:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该要看\N{\fs14}{\b0}you should read the letter.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.72,1:16:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你母亲让你喝酒吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Does she let you drink, your mother?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.61,1:16:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs14}{\b0}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.95,1:17:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过她不在这里\N{\fs14}{\b0}But she's not here.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.52,1:17:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么?\N{\fs14}{\b0}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.63,1:17:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是基安蒂红酒  告诉你\N{\fs14}{\b0}Well, it ain't Chianti, I'll tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.39,1:17:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是米酒   虽然是日本酒  不过味道不错\N{\fs14}{\b0}It's rice wine. It's Jap sake. But it does the trick.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.10,1:17:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底有多少这个鬼东西!\N{\fs14}{\b0}How much of this crap do you have anyway?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.55,1:17:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔  你那只耳朵是不是听不到?\N{\fs14}{\b0}You have a little trouble with that ear, don't you, Joe?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.33,1:17:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是内耳  我耳里的砧骨和镫骨已破损\N{\fs14}{\b0}Ah, real problem's the inner ear. It's anvils and stirrups and shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.25,1:17:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没办法保持平衡呢!\N{\fs14}{\b0}I'm a little out of balance.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.07,1:17:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天表现的很好  亚奇\N{\fs14}{\b0}You done good on that hill today, Yahzee.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.96,1:17:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  我做到了  不是吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yeah, I did, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.06,1:17:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我敢说我让你刮目相看了\N{\fs14}{\b0}I bet I surprised the shit out of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.08,1:18:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔  你也做了一件伟大的事\N{\fs14}{\b0}It was a noble thing that you did, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.09,1:18:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把勋章给了内里的妻子\N{\fs14}{\b0}To give your Silver Star to Nellie's wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.75,1:18:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不管勋章不勋章\N{\fs14}{\b0}I don't give a shit about medals.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.29,1:18:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得到第一枚勋章时\N{\fs14}{\b0}The first one they gave me...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.90,1:18:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把它丢到海里\N{\fs14}{\b0}I threw it into the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.10,1:18:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为何这么做呢?\N{\fs14}{\b0}What'd you get that one for?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.92,1:18:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我没死\N{\fs14}{\b0}For not dyin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.41,1:18:36.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我出生入死的15名弟兄也有\N{\fs14}{\b0}The 15 men who fought with me got decorated too.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.48,1:18:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全牺牲了  所以\N{\fs14}{\b0}For dying. So...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.52,1:18:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上尉出发前晚被杀了  而且\N{\fs14}{\b0}Lieutenant was killed the night before and...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.53,1:18:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有其他人愿意接手  所以 \N{\fs14}{\b0}none of the sergeants even made it out of the landing craft, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.40,1:18:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我留下负责  那是我第一次指挥\N{\fs14}{\b0}that left me in charge. It was my first command.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.68,1:19:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务是守住沼泽  可是又没有任何后援\N{\fs14}{\b0}Orders were to hold some shitty swamp marsh on the ass-end of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.80,1:19:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做到了\N{\fs14}{\b0}And I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.01,1:19:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我指挥下的\N{\fs14}{\b0}All of the men under my command...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.43,1:19:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期盼我的\N{\fs14}{\b0}men who trusted me...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.50,1:19:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求我撤退的所有弟兄\N{\fs14}{\b0}who begged me to pull back...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.70,1:19:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却没人能活下来\N{\fs14}{\b0}not one of them made it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.55,1:19:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只因为一个愚蠢的混蛋\N{\fs14}{\b0}Just one stupid asshole.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.33,1:19:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样  给了我银星勋章\N{\fs14}{\b0}And for that, they gave me the Silver Star.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.78,1:20:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们叫什么名字?\N{\fs14}{\b0}What were their names?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.45,1:20:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我可以把故事讲给后代听\N{\fs14}{\b0}It might be good to tell a story about 'em.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.65,1:20:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于他们的\N{\fs14}{\b0}You know, who they were...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.68,1:20:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,点点滴滴\N{\fs14}{\b0}and what they were like.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.78,1:20:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟这事有什么魔力让你这个纳瓦霍人想去知道\N{\fs14}{\b0}What a magical pile of Navajo horseshit. What the hell for?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.54,1:20:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去悼念他们\N{\fs14}{\b0}To honor them.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.53,1:20:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(印地安语)
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.36,1:20:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的精神\N{\fs14}{\b0}Their memory.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.17,1:20:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是你的错  乔\N{\fs14}{\b0}You know, it wasn't your fault, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.20,1:20:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不过是奉命行事罢了\N{\fs14}{\b0}You were just followin' orders.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.63,1:20:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.04,1:20:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个他妈的好军人\N{\fs14}{\b0}I'm a good fuckin' marine.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.12,1:20:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我有勋章\N{\fs14}{\b0}That's why they gave me this detail.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.52,1:20:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.79,1:20:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是个他妈的好军人\N{\fs14}{\b0}I'm a good fuckin' marine.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.53,1:21:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔\N{\fs14}{\b0}Joe
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.72,1:21:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-乔  -干吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}-Joe! -What?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.02,1:21:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却你的  乔 恩德斯\N{\fs14}{\b0}Goddamn you, Joe Enders!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.66,1:21:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是\N{\fs14}{\b0}Really.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.51,1:21:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\fs14}{\b0}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.64,1:21:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点  乔\N{\fs14}{\b0}Come on, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.56,1:21:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我扶你\N{\fs14}{\b0}I got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.74,1:23:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(印地安语)
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.09,1:23:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么玩意儿?\N{\fs14}{\b0}What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.06,1:23:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没醉  把烟掐了\N{\fs14}{\b0}I ain't that drunk, Yahzee. You cut that horseshit out.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.24,1:24:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们预期还有多远能抵达村庄? 完毕
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.88,1:24:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大约1500
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.12,1:24:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空中侦察回报没动静  应该很安全
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.36,1:24:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能的话需要提供干粮和信件  完毕
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.07,1:24:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把我爸的混合了瑞典调合物的草莓称为酸奶\N{\fs14}{\b0}I'm gonna mix my daddy's strawberries in this Swedish concoction called yoghurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.48,1:24:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪  美国将诞生一种新口味\N{\fs14}{\b0}God willin', America will develop the taste.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.72,1:24:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你呢  查理  战争过后你想过怎样的生活?\N{\fs14}{\b0}What about you, Charlie? What's life got in store for you after this mess?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.74,1:24:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牧羊\N{\fs14}{\b0}Sheep.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.76,1:24:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么牧羊?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Sheep?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.19,1:24:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像奇克的女朋友  绵羊\N{\fs14}{\b0}As in Chick's girlfriend, sheep?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.32,1:24:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查理家里拥有我们那片地区最大的羊群\N{\fs14}{\b0}Charlie's family owns the biggest flock in the Four Corners area.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.27,1:24:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的?\N{\fs14}{\b0}No shit?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.87,1:24:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-白马  你是个有钱人吧?  -将就吧\N{\fs14}{\b0}-You a rich man, Whitehorse? -We do OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.03,1:24:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀\N{\fs14}{\b0}Taxis.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.00,1:24:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我离开这个烂队  我就要成为百万富翁\N{\fs14}{\b0}A whole stinkin' fleet of 'em. That's how I'm making my millions.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.86,1:24:46.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后回到故乡去\N{\fs14}{\b0}And then I'm goin' back to the motherland.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.83,1:24:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要在圣托里尼的峭壁边  盖一栋别墅\N{\fs14}{\b0}I'm gonna build myself a villa on the cliffs of Santorini.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.49,1:24:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  圣托里尼  我的朋友\N{\fs14}{\b0}Ah, Santorini, my friends
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.74,1:24:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那才是享受\N{\fs14}{\b0}that's living.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.44,1:24:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来不错\N{\fs14}{\b0}Sounds nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.71,1:24:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚奇  那你呢?\N{\fs14}{\b0}What about you, Zee?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.39,1:24:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去教书\N{\fs14}{\b0}Thinkin' about teaching.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.88,1:25:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教书\N{\fs14}{\b0}Ah, teaching.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.92,1:25:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回报社会?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Bring a little something back to the reservation?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.58,1:25:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上\N{\fs14}{\b0}Actually,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.48,1:25:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实兴趣是想回报这个世界\N{\fs14}{\b0}more interested in bringing some of the reservation back to the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.76,1:25:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能在大学教书\N{\fs14}{\b0}Hoping to teach college.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.29,1:25:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教美国的历史\N{\fs14}{\b0}American history.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.77,1:25:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这正是我们需要的\N{\fs14}{\b0}Oh, that's just what we need.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.50,1:25:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚奇教大学生\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yahzee teachin' college boys...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.91,1:25:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道那会是什么情形\N{\fs14}{\b0}about Custer's scalpin' at Little Bighorn.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.19,1:25:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么卡森呢?\N{\fs14}{\b0}And what about Kit Carson,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.17,1:25:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可曾想替纳瓦霍人做些什么? \N{\fs14}{\b0}and what they did to the Navajo in the Long Walk?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.92,1:25:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇克  你有没听说过?\N{\fs14}{\b0} You ever read about that, Chick?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.29,1:25:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从没想过\N{\fs14}{\b0}Didn't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.48,1:25:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔  你呢?\N{\fs14}{\b0}How about you, Joe?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.21,1:25:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\fs14}{\b0}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.21,1:25:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切结束后你打算去做什么?\N{\fs14}{\b0}What are you doin' after this mess?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.35,1:25:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束后再说吧\N{\fs14}{\b0}It's gotta end sometime.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.92,1:25:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的乔\N{\fs14}{\b0}Dear Joe,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.55,1:25:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我们有个大好消息\N{\fs14}{\b0}we got great news today.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.89,1:25:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗斯福总统宣布夏威夷解放\N{\fs14}{\b0}President Roosevelt announced the end of blackouts on Hawaii.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.90,1:25:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们以为这一天 永远也不会来到\N{\fs14}{\b0}We thought the day would never come.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.64,1:25:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然十点以后仍然实行戒严\N{\fs14}{\b0}There's still a ten o'clock curfew,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.42,1:25:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但对我没什么影响\N{\fs14}{\b0}but it doesn't matter to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.65,1:26:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,12小时轮班  我累得除了写信  不能做别的事\N{\fs14}{\b0}After a 12-hour shift I'm too tired to do anything but write letters.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.06,1:26:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我预感战争会明朗化\N{\fs14}{\b0}There is a real sense that the war is going well...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.40,1:26:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就会结束\N{\fs14}{\b0}and could be over soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.83,1:26:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我越来越想你\N{\fs14}{\b0}I think about you more and more.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.07,1:26:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知你是死是活\N{\fs14}{\b0}If you're alive or dead out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.45,1:26:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每天查信\N{\fs14}{\b0}I check the mail every day,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.94,1:26:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从未有回音\N{\fs14}{\b0}knowing there's going to be an answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.79,1:26:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底有没有读我的信呢?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Are you reading these, Joe?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.72,1:26:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在听吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.99,1:26:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-左翼安全  -是个安全区域\N{\fs14}{\b0}-We're secure on the left side. -Area's secured.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.85,1:26:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建立防御阵地\N{\fs14}{\b0}Set up defense positions.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.81,1:26:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇克  晚上要戒严\N{\fs14}{\b0}Chick, bed 'em down for the night.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.01,1:26:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈里\N{\fs14}{\b0}Harri.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.45,1:27:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.87,1:27:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受伤了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.64,1:27:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿有些止痛药
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.32,1:28:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心  没事的
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.26,1:28:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢叔叔
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.58,1:28:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样听起来才比较像样点\N{\fs14}{\b0}That's startin' to sound like something.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.57,1:29:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没想到你还挺会画画\N{\fs14}{\b0}I didn't know you were an artist.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.33,1:29:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便乱涂的\N{\fs14}{\b0}Oh, it's stupid.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.04,1:29:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我小时候 \N{\fs14}{\b0}It's just...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.92,1:29:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我奶奶的餐桌上乱画\N{\fs14}{\b0}something I would do as a kid on my grandmother's kitchen table.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.63,1:29:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛮不错的\N{\fs14}{\b0}Well, it's nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.87,1:29:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是天主教徒吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}You Catholic?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.44,1:29:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前是\N{\fs14}{\b0}I used to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.64,1:29:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想我加入教会的情形\N{\fs14}{\b0}I was thinkin' about when they confirmed me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.91,1:29:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我八岁时  他们在我身上涂上圣水\N{\fs14}{\b0}I was eight, and they anointed me with the holy water.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.14,1:29:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得 \N{\fs14}{\b0}And I remember...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.53,1:29:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们告诉我我是神的战士\N{\fs14}{\b0}they told me I was a soldier of Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.39,1:30:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我该跳槽了\N{\fs14}{\b0}I guess somewhere along the way I must have switched units.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.22,1:30:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是油\N{\fs14}{\b0}It's oil.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.01,1:30:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Uh?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.23,1:30:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是圣水\N{\fs14}{\b0}They don't use holy water to confirm.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.71,1:30:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是油\N{\fs14}{\b0}They use oil.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.50,1:30:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也接受过洗礼\N{\fs14}{\b0}I was raised Catholic too.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.94,1:30:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在保留区内的外交使节学校\N{\fs14}{\b0}Mission school on the reservation.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.48,1:30:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好笑\N{\fs14}{\b0}It's funny.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.79,1:30:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神父不喜欢我们在说纳瓦霍话\N{\fs14}{\b0}Fathers didn't like us talking Navajo at Mass.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.74,1:30:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  那个星期天我忘了祷告\N{\fs14}{\b0}Of course, one Sunday I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.30,1:30:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们把我绑在地下室的散热器旁\N{\fs14}{\b0}They punished me by tying me to the radiator in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.86,1:30:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晒了两天\N{\fs14}{\b0}For two days.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.15,1:30:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那时也是八岁\N{\fs14}{\b0}I think I was eight too.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.74,1:30:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们现在允许你说纳瓦霍话了\N{\fs14}{\b0}Well, they're sure lettin' you talk Navajo now.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.87,1:30:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.11,1:30:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当这一切都结束\N{\fs14}{\b0}You know, when this is over,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.63,1:30:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你可以来我们的家乡\N{\fs14}{\b0}maybe you should come out to Navajo country.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.68,1:31:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纪念碑山谷\N{\fs14}{\b0}Monument Valley is...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.66,1:31:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美丽而宁静\N{\fs14}{\b0}a beautiful place. It's peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.49,1:31:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能去做些在部队里没做过的事\N{\fs14}{\b0}You know, we could do some things that you don't do in the Corps.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.09,1:31:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如骑马\N{\fs14}{\b0}Like ride horses,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.03,1:31:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃些美食\N{\fs14}{\b0}eat fry bread,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.12,1:31:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去狩猎\N{\fs14}{\b0}do some hunting...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.57,1:31:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骑马\N{\fs14}{\b0}Horses.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.78,1:31:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利桑那州貌似比较远\N{\fs14}{\b0}I don't know. It's a pretty long drive to Arizona.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.14,1:31:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但很值得\N{\fs14}{\b0}But it might be worth it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.40,1:31:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还可以来见见我的儿子\N{\fs14}{\b0}You know, you could meet my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.63,1:31:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就能见到那个\N{\fs14}{\b0}And he could meet Joe Enders,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.15,1:31:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时刻紧盯他父亲那骨瘦如柴的屁股的乔 恩德斯叔叔了\N{\fs14}{\b0}the guy who watched over Daddy's scrawny ass.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.39,1:31:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本  你一定是个好爸爸\N{\fs14}{\b0}You must be a very good father, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.60,1:31:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本\N{\fs14}{\b0}Ben.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.68,1:31:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以前从未这样叫我\N{\fs14}{\b0}You know, you've never called me that before.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.68,1:31:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩德斯\N{\fs14}{\b0}Enders.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.82,1:31:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个名字到底是什么意思?\N{\fs14}{\b0}What kind of name is that anyway?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.91,1:31:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自意大利的恩德罗尔菲尼 \N{\fs14}{\b0}It's Italian. Used to be Endrolfini...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.61,1:32:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝岛的前名\N{\fs14}{\b0}before some asshole at Ellis Island got hold of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.32,1:32:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上级要求解译员报到\N{\fs14}{\b0}Captain needs to code a message back to command post.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.85,1:32:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是那个印地安人?\N{\fs14}{\b0}You the Indian?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.27,1:32:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  正是\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yeah, I'm the Indian.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.76,1:32:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几分钟车程而已\N{\fs14}{\b0}It's just a few minutes' drive.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.08,1:32:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你马上可以回来\N{\fs14}{\b0}We'll get you back in no time.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.04,1:32:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冈尼 我要跟你谈谈\N{\fs14}{\b0}I need to speak with you, Gunny.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.70,1:32:45.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等片刻\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yeah. Give me a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.20,1:32:47.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天信  拿好了\N{\fs14}{\b0}Got this with the mail today.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.64,1:32:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不爽吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}You ever had pickled herring?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.40,1:32:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不干了\N{\fs14}{\b0}I need out.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.98,1:32:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在说什么?\N{\fs14}{\b0}What the hell are you talkin' about?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.39,1:32:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,细节\N{\fs14}{\b0}This detail.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.86,1:33:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的任务\N{\fs14}{\b0}My duty.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.99,1:33:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法做到\N{\fs14}{\b0}I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.77,1:33:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你  恩德斯\N{\fs14}{\b0}Well, I need you, Enders.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.35,1:33:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你曾经救过许多战友\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yeah. You've been saving a lot of marines.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.53,1:33:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我求指挥官您了  我不想干了\N{\fs14}{\b0}I'm requesting mast with battalion commander. I want out.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.78,1:33:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs14}{\b0}Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.91,1:33:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我\N{\fs14}{\b0}You and me
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.76,1:33:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有每个妈妈的宝贝儿子  我们都不干了\N{\fs14}{\b0}and every other mother's son. We all want out.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.56,1:33:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要东条英机和希特勒还活着\N{\fs14}{\b0}Well, as long as there's a Tojo and a Hitler out there
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.38,1:33:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就要继续打仗\N{\fs14}{\b0}we have to keep on fighting.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.81,1:33:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Is that understood?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.89,1:33:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有在听我说话\N{\fs14}{\b0}You're not hearing me.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.97,1:33:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听得很明白\N{\fs14}{\b0}I'm hearing you just fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.88,1:33:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在全世界都有战争\N{\fs14}{\b0}Now, there's a war goin' on worldwide,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.02,1:33:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会因你的意愿而停止\N{\fs14}{\b0}and it ain't bein' waged on your wants and wishes.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.58,1:33:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你可以稍事休息  这是命令\N{\fs14}{\b0}Now you get some sack time. That's an order.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.25,1:33:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\fs14}{\b0}Goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.47,1:33:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到\N{\fs14}{\b0}I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.06,1:33:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法执行我的任务\N{\fs14}{\b0}I can't perform my duty!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.94,1:34:09.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小宝贝\N{\fs14}{\b0}Hey there, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.82,1:34:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\fs14}{\b0}Hi. It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.80,1:34:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别哭  不会有事的\N{\fs14}{\b0}You don't have to cry. You're gonna be all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.60,1:34:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我送你一个礼物\N{\fs14}{\b0}Got a present for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.07,1:34:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是巧克力\N{\fs14}{\b0}This is chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.88,1:34:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃起来\N{\fs14}{\b0}You see, you eat it...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.61,1:34:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃喔\N{\fs14}{\b0}and it's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.42,1:34:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃\N{\fs14}{\b0}It's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.95,1:34:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要来一些吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}You want some?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.33,1:34:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次你得先嚼一嚼再咽喔\N{\fs14}{\b0}You'll have to chew it next time. Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.00,1:34:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈瑞肯  快走\N{\fs14}{\b0}Harrigan, go!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.05,1:35:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打过来了\N{\fs14}{\b0}Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.64,1:35:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑\N{\fs14}{\b0}Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.70,1:35:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走  快逃走啊!\N{\fs14}{\b0}Go! Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.22,1:35:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈瑞肯  让她快跑\N{\fs14}{\b0}Harrigan! Make her run!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.88,1:35:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快啊  给我\N{\fs14}{\b0}Come on! To me!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.87,1:35:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈瑞肯\N{\fs14}{\b0}Harrigan!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.24,1:36:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走啊  别呆在这儿\N{\fs14}{\b0}Come on, keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.69,1:37:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后退\N{\fs14}{\b0}Fall back!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.66,1:38:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救人  快救他\N{\fs14}{\b0}Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.82,1:38:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能让他们抓住\N{\fs14}{\b0}I can't let 'em take us.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.08,1:38:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么\N{\fs14}{\b0}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.07,1:39:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别杀他
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.29,1:39:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很重要
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.82,1:39:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们带他去审问
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.74,1:41:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩德斯\N{\fs14}{\b0}Enders!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.19,1:41:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找不到公牛和白马\N{\fs14}{\b0}I can't find Ox or Whitehorse.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.03,1:41:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看见他了吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Have you seen them?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.23,1:41:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就在那儿\N{\fs14}{\b0}He's over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.94,1:41:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 \N{\fs14}{\b0}Oh, shit...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.39,1:41:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是安全区域吗!\N{\fs14}{\b0}This was supposed to be a secured area!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.73,1:42:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事?\N{\fs14}{\b0}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.03,1:42:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我杀了他\N{\fs14}{\b0}I killed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.55,1:42:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你..你什么?\N{\fs14}{\b0}You...you what?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.16,1:42:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我扔手雷出去\N{\fs14}{\b0}I took my grenade and...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.78,1:42:16.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他炸死了\N{\fs14}{\b0}and I threw it and I blew him up.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.35,1:42:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你他妈的疯了吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}What the hell is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.88,1:42:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚奇\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yahzee!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.88,1:42:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚奇  不要\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yahzee! Yahzee, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.66,1:42:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起来\N{\fs14}{\b0}Get up!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.49,1:42:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fs14}{\b0}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.18,1:42:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你动手吧!\N{\fs14}{\b0}You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.47,1:42:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚奇\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yahzee.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.41,1:42:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他开枪\N{\fs14}{\b0}Let him go.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.45,1:42:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚奇  别这样\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yahzee, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.18,1:42:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点呀  为什么不开枪  来呀  开枪啊\N{\fs14}{\b0}Go on. Why can't...Come on. Do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.01,1:42:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开枪啊!\N{\fs14}{\b0}Do it!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.27,1:42:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fs14}{\b0}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.35,1:43:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们听说了白马的事了   亚奇
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.45,1:43:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会为他的名字 与事迹感到光荣
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.15,1:43:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了  查理  永别了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.14,1:43:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查理  永别了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.72,1:43:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白马 \N{\fs14}{\b0}You know, Whitehorse...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.40,1:43:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他救了我\N{\fs14}{\b0}he saved my bacon.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.52,1:44:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想早点对他好点就好了\N{\fs14}{\b0}Wonder what George Armstrong Custer would make of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.99,1:44:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得我的祖父坐在走廊说一些 \N{\fs14}{\b0}I remember my granddaddy sittin' on the porch talkin' about...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.96,1:44:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屠杀印地安人的事\N{\fs14}{\b0}huntin' Indians,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.17,1:44:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他曾经说过\N{\fs14}{\b0}like he was talkin' about gophers or somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.63,1:44:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个科曼奇人(印第安的一个种族)的耳朵\N{\fs14}{\b0}About gettin' paid three dollars...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.51,1:44:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能换3美元\N{\fs14}{\b0}per Comanche ear.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.87,1:44:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs14}{\b0}I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.59,1:44:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在想什么\N{\fs14}{\b0}Gets you thinkin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.31,1:44:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢?\N{\fs14}{\b0}Another 50 years,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.58,1:44:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再过50年\N{\fs14}{\b0}who knows,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.05,1:44:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我们会与日本人坐在一起\N{\fs14}{\b0}we could be sitting' down with the Nipponese.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.91,1:44:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝着日本米酒\N{\fs14}{\b0}Drinkin' their sake,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.07,1:44:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聊一些废话\N{\fs14}{\b0}shootin' the shit...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.38,1:44:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看别人的屁股\N{\fs14}{\b0}lookin' for somebody else's ass to kick.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.64,1:44:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想得太多了\N{\fs14}{\b0}You think too much.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.89,1:44:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次听别人这样说我\N{\fs14}{\b0}First time I ever been accused of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.40,1:45:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(印第安语)
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.14,1:45:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说过你不准自己四处乱跑\N{\fs14}{\b0}Thought I told you not to go traipsing around on your own.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.88,1:46:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查理在我儿子出生时\N{\fs14}{\b0}You know, Charlie blessed my son...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.66,1:46:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这方式祝福过他\N{\fs14}{\b0}in the Navajo way the day he was born.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.73,1:46:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他猜不透为什么牛仔要注意印第安人的后背\N{\fs14}{\b0}He wondered about cowboys watching Indians' backs.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.23,1:46:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他猜不透其中的奥妙\N{\fs14}{\b0}Something about it didn't seem right.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.18,1:46:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想查理就是查理\N{\fs14}{\b0}I thought it was Charlie just being Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.66,1:46:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他压根都不想参加这该死的战争\N{\fs14}{\b0}He didn't even want to come to this damn war.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.54,1:46:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我要他来的\N{\fs14}{\b0}I talked him into it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.87,1:46:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你做错了\N{\fs14}{\b0}Maybe you made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.22,1:46:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我们都死了\N{\fs14}{\b0}Maybe we all did.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.61,1:46:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本  我只是奉命行事\N{\fs14}{\b0}I was following orders, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.79,1:47:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接到的命令是保护密码\N{\fs14}{\b0}My orders were to protect the code.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.41,1:47:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们被抓\N{\fs14}{\b0}If one of you got caught,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.82,1:47:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被审讯\N{\fs14}{\b0}talked,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.30,1:47:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密码就没用了\N{\fs14}{\b0}the code would be useless.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.53,1:47:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在按命令行事  本\N{\fs14}{\b0}I was following orders, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.78,1:47:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了  乔\N{\fs14}{\b0}Course you were, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.17,1:47:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个他妈的好军人\N{\fs14}{\b0}You're a damn good fuckin' marine.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.80,1:47:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头儿想见你\N{\fs14}{\b0}The Viking wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.73,1:47:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要你马上去\N{\fs14}{\b0}He says right away.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.18,1:47:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你给每个人下达简令\N{\fs14}{\b0}I want you to brief everybody,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.29,1:47:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们明白发生了什么事\N{\fs14}{\b0} make clear what's happenin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.19,1:47:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs14}{\b0}All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.24,1:47:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没问题了\N{\fs14}{\b0}Got no problem with point, Gunny.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.51,1:47:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs14}{\b0}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.51,1:48:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在找我吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}You wanted to see me?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.92,1:48:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.60,1:48:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第八军团已经出发了\N{\fs14}{\b0}The 8th is moving out already...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.55,1:48:06.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要赶在他们前面\N{\fs14}{\b0}and we need to be ahead of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.84,1:48:09.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标是那边那块大岩石\N{\fs14}{\b0}The destination is that big piece of rock you see over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.60,1:48:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是这岛上最后一块根据地\N{\fs14}{\b0}The last defensible ridge on this island.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.46,1:48:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的想法是  我们搞定这个山头\N{\fs14}{\b0}Now, thinkin' is, we take the mount,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:16.92,1:48:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞班就归我们了\N{\fs14}{\b0}Saipan is pretty much ours.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.80,1:48:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天轰炸机炸过那块岩石\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yesterday, bombers beat the shit out of that rock.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.18,1:48:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些混蛋很顽强\N{\fs14}{\b0}The brass is nervous.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.42,1:48:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们预计会有很大的抵抗\N{\fs14}{\b0}They expected more resistance over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.92,1:48:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在他们想让我们去查看一下\N{\fs14}{\b0}Now they want us to go over and check it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.09,1:48:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他们现在要我们做什么\N{\fs14}{\b0}So where the hell they got us now?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.53,1:48:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到山上去\N{\fs14}{\b0}Goin' up the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.11,1:48:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侦查情况\N{\fs14}{\b0}Have ourselves a little peek.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.52,1:48:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个解译员也要到前线去\N{\fs14}{\b0}That codetalker is out front for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.77,1:48:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要的正是这种人\N{\fs14}{\b0}That's exactly where I need him to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.47,1:48:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你们之间还有隔阂\N{\fs14}{\b0}If there's still a problem between the two of you,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.23,1:48:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你们在此时此地解决问题\N{\fs14}{\b0}I would like to straighten that out, right here, right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.82,1:49:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题\N{\fs14}{\b0}No problem here, Gunny.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:03.30,1:49:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs14}{\b0}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.24,1:49:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但另外 \N{\fs14}{\b0}But there's still one here.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.00,1:49:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只须做你该做的  中士\N{\fs14}{\b0}You just do what you're supposed to do, Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.81,1:49:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要多做也不要少做\N{\fs14}{\b0}Nothing more, nothing less.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.97,1:49:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩德斯\N{\fs14}{\b0}Enders.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.22,1:49:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又有一封信\N{\fs14}{\b0}You got another letter.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.41,1:50:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动\N{\fs14}{\b0}Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.58,1:50:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天  我们走到该死的地雷区来了\N{\fs14}{\b0}Jesus Christ! We're in the middle of a goddamn minefield!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.67,1:50:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇克会带我们出去的\N{\fs14}{\b0}Chick's gonna get us out.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.19,1:50:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧? 奇克\N{\fs14}{\b0}Right, Chick?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.22,1:50:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然会\N{\fs14}{\b0}Sure I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.66,1:50:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在奇克后面排成一排\N{\fs14}{\b0}One line after Chick.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:01.25,1:51:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕帕斯\N{\fs14}{\b0}Pappas.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.85,1:51:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕帕斯\N{\fs14}{\b0}Pappas.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.30,1:51:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走啊  格里克\N{\fs14}{\b0}Move, Greek.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.84,1:51:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一踩到地雷怎么办?\N{\fs14}{\b0}I'm gonna get my fuckin' balls blown off out here!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:21.52,1:51:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚奇  停下来\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yahzee! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.21,1:51:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲出去\N{\fs14}{\b0}Move out!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.97,1:52:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚奇\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yahzee!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.48,1:52:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打得好  帕帕斯\N{\fs14}{\b0}Nice shootin', Pap.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:08.27,1:53:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第八军团在行进了\N{\fs14}{\b0}The 8th's movin' in.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.04,1:53:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得查查另一个边\N{\fs14}{\b0}We'd better check out the other side.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.11,1:53:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解\N{\fs14}{\b0}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.12,1:53:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧?\N{\fs14}{\b0}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.53,1:53:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇克你走左边  恩德斯你走右边\N{\fs14}{\b0}Chick, take the left flank. Enders, go right.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.48,1:53:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持30步互相掩护\N{\fs14}{\b0}We'll cover you with a 30.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:19.16,1:53:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-遵命  -好了吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}-On it. -All right?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.19,1:53:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  行动\N{\fs14}{\b0}OK, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.60,1:53:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上\N{\fs14}{\b0}Move!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:44.92,1:53:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈佐斯特\N{\fs14}{\b0}Hjelmstad!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.34,1:53:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去帮他\N{\fs14}{\b0}Help him up!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.23,1:53:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冈尼\N{\fs14}{\b0}Gunny!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.34,1:53:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fs14}{\b0}Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.14,1:54:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天\N{\fs14}{\b0}Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.57,1:54:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔! 乔!\N{\fs14}{\b0}Joe! Joe!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.07,1:54:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撕开衣服\N{\fs14}{\b0}Tear him open.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.26,1:54:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要吗啡吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}You want morphine?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:17.07,1:54:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要吗啡吗?\N{\fs14}{\b0}You want morphine?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.56,1:54:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要\N{\fs14}{\b0}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:22.66,1:54:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会没事的  长官\N{\fs14}{\b0}You'll be all right, sir.
